4️⃣ Printer Troubleshooting Workflow
User symptom: “Printer is offline” or “Nothing prints.”

🧩 Step-by-step workflow
Check Print Spooler service

Restart if stuck

Clear print queue

Stuck jobs block all printing

Verify printer IP

Ping printer

If unreachable → network issue

Check printer driver

Wrong driver = offline printer

Check printer port

Ensure TCP/IP port matches printer IP

Check user permissions

Some printers require group membership

Reinstall printer

Use correct driver package

🎯 Resolution examples
Restart spooler

Fix incorrect printer IP

Reinstall printer with correct driver

Clear corrupted print queue
